|------|--------|---------|
| `server/api/cards.js` | **Create** | Express Router вЂ” routes at `/cards` and `/cards/:id` |
| `server/test/cards.test.mjs` | **Create** | Integration tests (9 describe blocks, ~25 test cases) |
| `server/index.js` | **Modify** | `app.use('/api', cardsRouter)` before 404 handler |
| `server/package.json` | **Modify** | Add supertest dev dep; extend test script |

## Reusable Utilities (from `server/db/queries.js`)

- `getCards()` вЂ” returns all cards with nested `comments` array
- `createCard(data)` вЂ” `{ title, assignee?, column?, description? }` в†’ raw card row (no `comments` field вЂ” POST handler adds `comments: []` manually)
- `updateCard(id, data)` вЂ” partial update, throws `NotFoundError` if card absent
- `deleteCard(id)` вЂ” throws `NotFoundError` if card absent, returns `true`
- `NotFoundError` вЂ” use `instanceof` check in catch blocks to return 404
- `initDb(':memory:')` / `closeDb()` вЂ” test DB lifecycle (module-level singleton)

---

## Verification

### Run tests
```bash
