```js
app.use('/api', cardsRouter);   // в†ђ mount at /api, NOT /api/cards
```

**`server/api/cards.js`**:
```js
router.get('/cards', ...);      // в†’ GET  /api/cards
router.post('/cards', ...);     // в†’ POST /api/cards
router.patch('/cards/:id', ...);// в†’ PATCH  /api/cards/:id
